Title: Technical Remarks and Comments on the UV/IR-Mixing Problem of a

Noncommutative Scalar Quantum Field TheoryAuthors: F. Aigner, M. Hillbrand, J. Knapp, G. Milovanovic, V. Putz, R.

Sch\"ofbeck, M. SchwedaComments: 9 pages, uses bbm

In this letter we will dicuss the possibility of a resummation procedure inorder to cure the UV/IR-mixing problem of noncommutative field theories. Themethod is presented for a scalar phi^4 theory on Euclidean space. Finally, wesketch the idea of resummation for U(1)-gauge theories.